<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.9.4">
<l>tuṉṟōḷit tukilpaṭalan tuṉṉiyeṅkum māḷikaimēl</l>
<l>niṉṟāra vāṉmūṭum nīḷcelvat tirunaṟaiyūr</l>
<l>maṉṟārak kuṭamāṭi varaiyeṭuttu maḻaitaṭutta</l>
<l>kuṉṟārun tiraṭōḷaṅ kuraikaḻalē yaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirunaṟaiyūr of vast wealth where multitudes of banners, fixed in rows,</l>
<l>Crowding and standing everywhere on mansions, when unfurled,</l>
<l rend="indent">obscured the sky,</l>
<l>O heart, take refuge in the rattling [war] anklets</l>
<l rend="indent">of the one with mountain-like, strong shoulders</l>
<l>Who blocked the rain, lifting a mountain, having danced with pots</l>
<l rend="indent">so the village square filled.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
